Ru-yi: W-w-w... What'll we do, Sophie?

Tindoiimu: These people are innocent. Don't drag them into this. I'll go with you, just let them go.
Sophie: Tindoiimu!?
Alliance Soldier: Are you for real?
Tindoiimu: Whatever you're going to do, just do it.
Alliance Soldier: ...All right.
Sophie: Tindoiimu!
Tindoiimu: Forget about me, just get out of here...
Alliance Soldier: Who said they could leave?

Sophie: How can you do this to us! She surrendered already!
